Welcoming guests to the 11th Bola Tinubu Colloquium, Ambode describe Tinubu as a man of high political dexterity, a dogged leader and man of undaunted courage. He expressed confidence that the APC was spreading its progressive tentacles further into the country, while Nigerians are looking forward to moving to the next level. He said the theme of the Colloquium, Next Level: work for the people was choosen to coincide with the times when the country was on the threshold of greatness.  Osinbajo, others attend 11th Tinubu Colloquium The International Conference Centre, Abuja is a beehive of activities as Nigerians from all works of life converge at the centre to celebrate the National Leader of the All Progressives Congress, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu as he marks his 66th birthday.
